




C-x 3 : open split window on right
C-x 0 : close focus split window
C-x o : focus on next window

C-x C-b : buffers list

S-+ : switch next buffer
S-- : switch previous buffer


M-x (alt + x ) shell : open terminal shell


C-+ : zom out
C-- : zom in

C-r : read only

C-f : search forward
C-b : search backward

C-n : open new file

C-x C-s : save file
C-x C-c : close buffer

C-c c : copy
C-c v : past
C-c x : cut

 
C-g : quit the keybind or the comand

